      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOLLYHILL KING (6) jumped well to win over the 450m at this track two runs back then prominent throughout when finishing second at this track last start. Goes very well from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from 11 starts. Top chance in this line up. DROOPYS LINK (5) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 450m behind Slingshot Poppy (27.91) in a OR3. Was in the money prior to that. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. One of the better chances. ROMEO HANYU (4) is a smart dog who pinged the lids from trap four and cleared the pack early, leading throughout to win (27.27) at this track in IV over 450m. Superior out of the boxes and will be in the firing line early. Must be included in calculations. FRENCHYARROW (3) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when third (27.40) in a OR3 over 450m at this track.",
